works.description: My blog post "How To Access Facebook When it is Blocked in School College Or Office" is infringed by the text excerpted on the site, beginning with the text "Did you try to access Facebook when you are in school, college or office? You must found that you are blocked when you are trying to access them, mainly the social networking sites. Most of the organizations block social networking websites to prevent people from getting access to Facebook, Orkut etc. where people spent a lot of time. If you are addicted in Facebook or Orkut like me then you must have tried some methods to get access to those blocked websites."
